    "path": "src/server/step/relay",
    "name": "relay",
    "purpose": "Owns server-side tracking of relay work as a submodule of step, mirroring the execution submodule structure with panic-stub placeholders pending implementation. Relay is intended to capture one relay keyed by its RelaySignature, record the spawning step, accumulate ordered output chunks, and finalize against the expected update count. RelayHub holds a Mutex<HashMap<RelaySignature, Relay>>, is intended to spawn relay steps, route RelayEvent Update/Status events into the tracked Relay, emit StepEvent back to the step layer on completion, and report per-signature status.",
    "changeStatus": "added"
  },
